{"tid":1696001,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iphone 11s 萬二起標不是夢~iPhone SE2將采用10層板SLP，11s 單價提高","createTime":"2019-11-06T02:37:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T07:07:12.000Z","uid":141060,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ee77e5e4bc872494b4498ba66d231b18260fbcfa","tid":1696001,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T02:37:16.000Z","msg":"11月6日消息 昨日晚間，天風國際分析師郭明錤發布了最新蘋果研究。<br />\n<br />\n報告指出，蘋果自2019年第三季度末開始停售配備Any-layer HDI主板的iPhone機型 (包括iPhone 7系列與更早機型)。同期，iPhone機型開始全部配備單價更高的SLP。<br />\n<br />\n報告預測，2020年上半年發售的iPhone SE2將采用10層板、線寬線距為25&ndash;30&mu;m的SLP。且配備Any-layer HDI的較低價iPhone機型在2019年第一季度至第三季度出貨量約為2000萬部，考慮到iPhone SE2定位也在較低價產品，預計iPhone SE2在2020年出貨量至少為2000萬部（樂觀情況為3000萬部）。<br />\n<br />\n報告重申了之前的預測，2020年下半年的新款iPhone全部支持5G，SLP面積將增加10&ndash;15%，SLP單價將增加30&ndash;35%。同時，SLP將為支持5G而提升規格，包括更低的介值耗損、更低的熱膨脹系數與更高的玻璃轉移點溫度。報告指出，2020款5G iPhone SLP單價將相比iPhone 11系列提高30&ndash;35%。"},{"pid":"93620f24f62865998e5d1637c6b646f7f99f72a7","tid":1696001,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T02:59:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b538a952bd08750337be5ee9b95802f7d2e2f34","tid":1696001,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T03:02:00.000Z","msg":"有冇touch id <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7739dcf4ac0dcbdf62f03f5cfbe482e278cb0156","tid":1696001,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7b538a952bd08750337be5ee9b95802f7d2e2f34","tid":1696001,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T03:02:00.000Z","msg":"有冇touch id <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T03:05:14.000Z","msg":"應該有 se2"},{"pid":"5fb08008e98f9cbbceb241ae9498587307b070ef","tid":1696001,"uid":61094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T03:08:21.000Z","msg